Package: phylopq
Title: Phylogenetic Analysis for 'phyloseq' Objects
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Adrien", "Taudière", , "adrien.taudiere@zaclys.net", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1088-1182"))
Description: A phylogenetic analysis layer for 'phyloseq' objects within the
    'pqverse' ecosystem. Provides helpers for tree construction from
    taxonomy tables, phylogenetic distance metrics, phylogeny-aware
    ordinations and visualisations, and integration with external
    phylogenetic placement tools. Built on top of 'phyloseq', 'ape' and
    'MiscMetabar'.
License: AGPL-3
URL: https://adrientaudiere.github.io/phylopq/,
    https://github.com/adrientaudiere/phylopq
BugReports: https://github.com/adrientaudiere/phylopq/issues
